    "content" : "<span style=\"font-weight: bold\"><span style=\"color: #FF0000\">Front door hinge pin repair - Part 2</span></span>\n<br>\n<br>Pic of the rivets removed from the door…\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1069.photobucket.com/user/midwestdubber1/media/004.2_zpspodo5bpx.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1069.photobucket.com/albums/u463/midwestdubber1/004.2_zpspodo5bpx.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<br>The next step was to mark out and cut two sections which would allow the hinge to be removed from the door. I used a small cut-off wheel in a Dremel to make the cuts. The sheet metal was then carefully peeled back and the hinge removed…\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1069.photobucket.com/user/midwestdubber1/media/005_zpsm2cktutd.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1069.photobucket.com/albums/u463/midwestdubber1/005_zpsm2cktutd.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1069.photobucket.com/user/midwestdubber1/media/006_zpskjdoqxte.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1069.photobucket.com/albums/u463/midwestdubber1/006_zpskjdoqxte.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s1069.photobucket.com/user/midwestdubber1/media/007_zpsw9tswuqn.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i1069.photobucket.com/albums/u463/midwestdubber1/007_zpsw9tswuqn.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>",
